Examples

library(tidyverse)

istar <- LFQService::ionstar
istar$data <- istar$data %>% dplyr::filter(protein_Id %in% sample(protein_Id, 100))
lfqdata <- LFQData$new(istar$data, istar$config)
sum <- lfqdata$get_Summariser()
sum$hierarchy_counts()

#> # A tibble: 1 x 3
